Everything you need to know about Opinion Kings.

Contact us

01

Is this gambling?

No. These are event-based financial contracts structured within regulatory frameworks.

02

Is this legal?

We are building under a compliance-first, U.S.-regulated structure.

03

Is it real money?

Yes. Live trading will use real capital upon regulatory launch.

04

When does it launch?

Beta access begins with early waitlist members.

05

How do I move up the waitlist?

Invite friends using your referral link and unlock rewards.

06

How can I get support if I run into issues?

We’re here to help. If you have questions, you can reach us directly at hello@kadirov.design. We usually respond within 24 hours.
